----------------------------------------------------------------
 THE API (BACKEND)
----------------------------------------------------------------

  All data is handled by PHP files in the /api/ folder:

  File                  What it does
  ------------------    --------------------------------------
  login.php             Checks credentials, returns user data
  signup.php            Creates new account (auto-creates
                        tutor profile if role is tutor)
  tutors.php            Returns tutor list — approved only,
                        all, or all for chat
  profile.php           Gets or saves a tutor's profile
  student_profile.php   Gets or saves a student's profile
  sessions.php          Gets sessions and creates/updates them
  materials.php         Lists materials, handles uploads and
                        deletes
  messages.php          Gets conversations, sends/deletes msgs
  users.php             Lists all users, handles deletion
  earnings.php          Earnings breakdown for tutor or admin
  stats.php             Live platform stats (counts)


